<p>I want to do the exact same thing when something goes wrong with authentication.</p>
<p>Open up the <code>TokenControllerTest</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="b167c530e4">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
            <span class="fa fa-clipboard js-activate-clipboard" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Copy Code" data-placement="top"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
                        <span class="js-expand-all" data-range="1-33" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Show All Lines" data-placement="top">
